<plot>Fred works in a garage as a mechanic where he is surrounded by what comforts him; machines. He would rather live his life people free with only cars to fix. One day, a neighbor's misfortune changes Fred's life forever. This event forces Fred to face his fears and change what is missing in his life. Mechanic is a quiet and humorous look into how one introverted and humble man re-discovers the world around him.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?363166</url></doc>
